Products.Name: Birds Eye Southern Blue Whiting Original Crumb
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Birds Eye Southern Blue Whiting Original Crumb' has a supply limit of 10. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.SmallFormatDescription: Birds Eye Southern Blue Whiting Original Crumb
Products.FullDescription: Birds Eye Southern Blue Whiting Original Crumb
Products.RichDescription:
Southern Blue Whiting in a delicious original crumb.

Southern Blue Whiting is found in the southern oceans and caught at depths up to 800m. Subtle, sweet flavour.

Recognised by its unique blue scales, it is renowned for its versatility and sweet, delicate flavour.

Delicate texture.

We like to bring you the very best, that's why this birds eye southern blue whiting is of the highest quality, caught fresh from the ocean with all natural ingredients. 

Fish is one of the best natural sources of long chain omega-3 and our premium fish fillets are a convenient way to get them just as nature intended.

At Birds Eye Australia we're proud to be contributing to feeding Australians with our delicious, frozen seafood ranges including our Fish Finger, Oven Bake and Crumbed Fillet ranges that you've come to love and trust. We have recently changed the labelling of some of our frozen seafood products from 'Made in Australia' to 'Packed in Australia'. Our products are the same delicious products that are proudly processed at our factory in Kelso NSW. You will start to see these changes on our packaging from mid-November 2020 through to March 2021. Products will be available featuring both a “Made in” and “Packed in” claim during this period.

Products.RichDescription:
WEIS ICE CREAM DAIRY FREE DARK CHOCOLATE 1 LTR
Weis Dark Chocolate Dessert is beautifully rich and indulgent... and it's dairy free too! Perfect on its own, in smoothies, or alongside fruits or other desserts. This is a delicious alternative to ice cream for people looking for a gluten and dairy free treat! Our deliciously refreshing sorbet range is sure to be a hit in any home, particularly over the warmer summer months! Weis Sorbets are dairy free, made with real fruit, and have no artificial colours or flavours. Even better, they are absolutely delicious. Our classic sorbet are a delightful and refreshing treat, great for after dinner or as a summertime snack. Or, if you are looking for something a little different, we now have a range of exotic sorbets. Weis Sorbet Exotics are sorbets with a twist! They are packed with interesting fruit and flavour combinations to create a truly surprising sorbet sensation! At Weis our products are based on recipes, so the focus is on the subtle blending of real ingredients and ultimately the taste. Our knowledge and expertise in sourcing and working with all different kinds of fruits, premium grade nuts and natural ingredients enables us to create unique combinations and taste experiences. Today, the world-class Weis range of Bars, Ice Creams, Frozen Yoghurts and Sorbets is loved across Australia and around the world. We're passionate about surprising and delighting our customers with exceptional quality ingredients and fabulous flavour combinations.
Weis Dark Chocolate Dessert is beautifully rich and indulgent
A delicious dairy free frozen treat
Enjoy either on its own or paired with yourfavourite desserts
Gluten free and vegan friendly
No artificial flavours or colours
Made in Australia since 1957
